note right
  <b>Features</b>
  ----
  Global reference data
  Burdened = Base x (1 + Burden%)
  Burdened rate is calculated,
  never manually entered
  ----
  Code immutable after creation
  Rate changes affect future only
  ----
  Admin only: add, edit, toggle
  All roles: view
end note

